"title": "7398: New Moon festival",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7398",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The festival which marked the consecration to God of each new month in the year.</p>\n<h2>New Moon festivals were required under the Mosaic law</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:11\">NUM 28:11</a></strong></p>\n<h2>New Moon festivals were times of celebration</h2>\n<h3>They were marked by blowing of trumpets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:10\">NUM 10:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:3\">PSA 81:3</a></p>\n<h3>They were celebrated with offerings</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:11-Num28:15\">NUM 28:11–28:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr23:30-1Chr23:31\">1CH 23:30–23:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:4\">2CH 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:12-2Chr8:13\">2CH 8:12–8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:3\">2CH 31:3</a> <em>reformed temple worship under Hezekiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:32-Neh10:33\">NEH 10:32–10:33</a> <em>New Moon festivals were restored on the return from exile</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek45:17\">EZK 45:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:1\">EZK 46:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:3\">EZK 46:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:6\">EZK 46:6</a></p>\n<h3>They were times when normal work ceased</h3>\n<p>David was to dine with Saul:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:5\">1SA 20:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:18\">1SA 20:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:24\">1SA 20:24</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:23\">2KI 4:23</a> <em>the Shunammite woman and her husband</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:5\">AMO 8:5</a> <em>Some saw them as a hindrance to business.</em></p>\n<h2>A wrong inner attitude at New Moon celebrations incurs God's anger</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:13-Isa1:14\">ISA 1:13–1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:11\">HOS 2:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:7\">HOS 5:7</a></p>\n<h2>NT reference to the New Moon festival</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:16-Col2:17\">COL 2:16–2:17</a></strong></p>",
